snippet: The fourth fight between Juan Manuel Marquez and Manny Pacquiao provided the first clear outcome but still raised no shortage of questions.
abstract: Greg Bishop On Boxing column on Juan Manuel Marquez defeating Manny Pacquiao with sixth-round knockout; says that fourth fight between Marquez and Pacquiao provided first clear outcome but still raised no shortage of questions.
lead_paragraph: The fourth fight between Juan Manuel Marquez and Manny Pacquiao provided the first clear outcome but still raised no shortage of questions.

headline.seo: Marquez-Pacquiao Result, a Knockout, Leaves Much Unanswered
headline.main: Despite Knockout, Fight Leaves Much Unanswered
